            <h3 class="pt-4 mb-2 text-2xl text-center">Business community</h3>
            <p class="px-2 text-sm text-gray-700">There are people in <strong>#business</strong> channel who could help you with your fresh idea and point you to the right direction. They passed almost all levels of German bureaucracy and could give you a free, non-binding advice.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center">
            <div class="rounded overflow-hidden shadow-lg xl:w-2/6">
