                </a>
                <div class="px-6 py-4">
                    <p class="text-gray-700 text-base">
                        Order craft beverages online. Craft beer, gin, whiskey, rum, grain, coffee, espresso, wine, sodas. Buy over 600 products directly from the manufacturer.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
